HEADWORD: Circumduce
<hw>Cir`cum*duce"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Circumduct</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld> <def>To declare
